NAME
    P5U::Command::cttail - grep through the last 1000 cpan testers reports

SYNOPSIS
     $ p5u cttail --author=TOBYINK

     $ p5u cttail --reporter=TOBYINK

     $ p5u cttail -d Moose -f '%(grade)s for %(perlversion)s on %(platform)s'

DESCRIPTION
    Simple tool to grep <http://metabase.cpantesters.org/tail/log.txt>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs to
    <http://rt.cpan.org/Dist/Display.html?Queue=P5U-Command-cttail>.

SEE ALSO
    p5u, P5U::Command::Testers.

